{
  "stem": "23428.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He-- he was sort of a free-thinker and had lived in Berlin and was a-- sort of a political nudist in the-- in the '20s, had enjoyed the free atmosphere of Berlin.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in fact, I think he was the only one who was not religious and talked a lot about need to stay firm when they finally put him against the wall.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I don't remember his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was enough room just to-- like sardines, to stretch out next to the next guy.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the floor, right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the prison situation ended by somebody opening the door and say, come out for transport.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were loaded onto-- onto a truck, back of a truck, with armed SS people standing at the exit, and were driven to the train station, put into a cattle car, and taken to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, as I say, in this cattle car, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we also found my father and-- and my mother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So actually, the four of us, for a few hours-- well, I don't know how long it took, maybe half a day-- could be together once more.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were lined up, I think, before-- before actually getting onto the car, there were lineups where we could see them, of course.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] instructed us, in fact, to take the best care we could of my mother, by [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] giving her as much hope and self-confidence as we could.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I mean, that was even more crowded than the prison, in the sense that nobody could lie down.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, there was just enough room for people to stand up like sardines.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was really filled up.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
